<plot>In this game you take on the role of the nobleman Samuel Gordon, who returns after 20 years to the manor called Black Mirror where he spent most of his life. He returns back to remember William Gordon who had meant much for him. Samuel is the only one who doesn't believe William's death was an accident. The Black Mirror adventure is very mysterious and is divided to six parts.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?544401</url></doc>
